data.description: Welcome to this gorgeous home. This residence is centrally located in Snellville, Ga. The two-story home located in a cul-de-sac within The Rosebud Park subdivision features a formal living and dining room, powder room, kitchen, and breakfast area on the main level. Large master bedroom and three additional bedrooms with tons of closet space and vaulted ceilings in all rooms on the second level. The owner's bath features   a beautiful vanity, garden tub, shower and separate closet space. This home is situated in a convenient and friendly neighborhood with schools and shopping nearby. With the right love and attention, this home has the potential to become a delightful place of peace for your family.
